title: FS: T206 Dutch Revelle SGC 96!! Why not a 98?
author: CMIZ5290

posts.post_title: FS: T206 Dutch Revelle SGC 96!! Why not a 98?
posts.post_content:
Card is gem mint as much as a 100 year old card can be, perfect corners and centering. One of the tougher SLers as well! Spotless Old Mill back, it simply does not get better than this card. It looks like it has been in a time capsule.  Offered at $15K, possibly entertain T206 trades, thanks...
